                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The elastic scattering",
                "cross sections can obtained from the calculated proton",
                "Rutherford scattering cross section and the formula is",
                "showed as equation (1) in J,NIM/B,268,3373,201008."
              ]
            }
          ],
